ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act
PrecisOrder amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE SPECIES AT RISK ACT (SARA) in order to reclassify Carmine Shiner, Rainbow Smelt (Lake Utopia large-bodied population), and Rainbow Smelt (Lake Utopia small-bodied population) from threatened to endangered on Schedule 1, as set out in the assessments of Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada (COSEWIC).
